Project Manager management ZF is a global technology company supplying systems for passenger cars, commercial vehicles and industrial technology, enabling the next generation of mobility.

ZF allows vehicles to see, think and act. In the four technology domains of Vehicle Motion Control, Integrated Safety, Automated Driving, and Electric Mobility, ZF offers comprehensive product and software solutions for established vehicle manufacturers and newly emerging transport and mobility service providers. ZF electrifies a wide range of vehicle types. With its products, the company contributes to reducing emissions, protecting the climate and enhancing safe mobility.


** Project Manager**

Country/Region:   CN               Location:     Qingdao, SD, CN, 266108   

Req ID 69501 Qingdao, China  


**Your Tasks**

* Lead application projects to mass production in accordance with our internal processes (GDPEP) ;  
* Define program scope, timing and baseline, project team and SteerCo. Members. Lead the cross-functional project team; Establish the program timing plan based on the program milestones requirement;   
* Report the program status to leaders and update the program report;  
* Escalate the program issues to leaders on time to ensure the program smooth run;   
* Manage project budget and financial KPI's to ensure profitability of the project.  


**Your Profile**

* Bachelor degree is a must; Mechanical/Electrical Engineering background is preferable;   
* At least 3+ years PM working experience with full program lifecycle run in Automotive industry, having global program experience;   
* Good English skill at both oral and writing; Germany is a plus;  
* Logic thoughts, good communication skills and team player, fast learning;  
* Strong communication, personality / resilience, initiative, cultural competence.  


**Be part of our ZF team and apply now!**

